          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The content mode specifies how the cached bitmap of the viewâ€™s layer is adjusted when the viewâ€™s bounds change. This property is often used to implement resizable controls. Instead of redrawing the contents of the view every time, you can use this property to specify that you want to scale the contents (either with or without distortion) or pin them to a particular spot on the view."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "aside",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "You can always force the contents of a view to be redrawn by calling the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uiview/1622437-setneedsdisplay"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " or "
                },
                {
                  "type": "reference",
                  "isActive": true,
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uiview/1622587-setneedsdisplayinrect"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " method. "
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "style": "note",
          "name": "Note"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "For a list of values you can assign to this property, see "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uiviewcontentmode"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". The default value of this property is "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/uikit/uiviewcontentmode/uiviewcontentmodescaletofill"
            },
            {
